  <brief_title>Trial of Adjuvant Sutent for Patients With High Risk Urothelial Carcinoma After Neoadjuvant Chemotherapy and Cystectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase II Trial of Adjuvant Sutent for Patients With High Risk Urothelial Carcinoma After Neoadjuvant Chemotherapy and Cystectomy</official_title>
