  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether sutent (sunitinib)is effective in
      preventing tumor recurrence in patients with high risk bladder cancer who have previously
      had chemotherapy and cystectomy (bladder removal).

      A 4 month supply of the drug is given to patients beginning 2-3 months after bladder
      removal. The patients are followed up to 2 years.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
